rows.label: qev065504_MSG0001
rows.name:
Rrrf! All my missions have been so freakin' dull lately.
I'm feeling so pent up![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0002
rows.name:
Doesn't anybody need like...I dunno, a pack of
indigens punched in the face or something?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Sara-Ariel how she would describe herself.

rows.label: qev065504_SEL0021
rows.name:
Tell Sara-Ariel that you know a
guy who wants to meet her.

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0003
rows.name:
I'm not the sharpest tool in the shed, but I've got more
pep than I know what to do with. Oh, and I can mop
the floor with any guy when it comes to piloting Skells![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0004
rows.name:
During our last scrimmage, I took out everybody else
on my team single-handed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0005
rows.name:
Am I single? With my personality? Ha ha ha ha!
I've been single since birth, girl.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0006
rows.name:
Doesn't bother me, though. I'm too busy kicking butt
to be fawning over some guy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0007
rows.name:
Whaaat?! There's a guy who wants to meet me?
...Seriously?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0008
rows.name:
But like...to talk, right? I mean, he doesn't want to
challenge me to a fight or anything? Because he'd lose.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0009
rows.name:
Weeell...yeah, sure. Okay. I want to meet anybody
brave enough to try me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0010
rows.name:
Whoa! He's pretty good looking.
Are you sure he's really into me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0011
rows.name:
You think he really sees me as a woman and not
just...something else?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065504_MSG0012
rows.name: If so, I... Man, that'd be great. I'd be really happy.[ST:wait ]
